ices without notification to you.</span></p>\n<p style=\"position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:479.75px\" class=\"cls_003\"><span class=\"cls_003\">14.</span><span class=\"cls_004\"> Right of Set Off.</span><span class=\"cls_003\">  You agree that nanopay is authorized at any time to setoff or recoup any liability for which it</span></p>\n<p style=\"position:absolute;left:72.00px;top:491.75px\" class=\"cls_003\"><span class=\"cls_003\">determines you are liable to us. nanopay shall not be required to provide you prior notice of the exercise of such</span></p>\n<p style=\"position:absolute;left:72.00px;top:503.75px\" class=\"cls_003\"><span class=\"cls_003\">set off right.</span></p>\n<p style=\"position:absolute;left:54.75px;top:527.75px\" class=\"cls_003\"><span class=\"cls_003\">15.</span><span class=\"cls_004\"> Our Relationship Is One of Electronic Commerce</span><span class=\"cls_003\">.</span></p>\n<p style=\"position:absolute;left:72.75px;top:551.75px\" class=\"cls_003\"><span class=\"cls_003\">15.01.You consent to the provision of required disclosures to you in electronic format. If you do not consent to</span></p>\n<p style=\"position:absolute;left:102.75px;top:563.75px\" class=\"cls_003\"><span class=\"cls_003\">electronic disclosure of these documents, then you may not use the Platform. Your consent applies to all</span></p>\n<p style=\"position:absolute;left:102.75px;top:575.75px\" class=\"cls_003\"><span class=\"cls_003\">of the documents we provide to you electronically in connection with this Agreement, including receipts</span></p>\n<p style=\"position:absolute;left:102.75px;top:587.75px\" class=\"cls_003\"><span class=\"cls_003\">and notices.</span></p>\n<p style=\"position:absolute;left:72.75px;top:611.75px\" class=\"cls_003\"><span class=\"cls_003\">15.02.Access to electronic disclosures will be provided by way of the Internet. Your history of use is available</span></p>\n<p style=\"position:absolute;left:102.75px;top:623.75px\" class=\"cls_003\"><sp